net.minecraftforge.registries

Class ClearableRegistry<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraft.util.registry.Registry<T>
      • net.minecraft.util.registry.MutableRegistry<T>
        • net.minecraftforge.registries.ClearableRegistry<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, IObjectIntIterable<T>

    public class ClearableRegistry<T>
extends MutableRegistry<T>
    A IRegistry implementation that allows for removing of objects. This is a internal helper class used by Forge for managing things that reset during Server initialization.
